<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Últimos eventos</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link
  href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css"
  rel="stylesheet"
/>

<link rel="stylesheet" href="/general/css/colors.css">

  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      background: var(--primary-color);
      padding: 40px;
      color: #333;
    }

    .gallery {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 30px;
    }

    .card {
      position: relative; 
      background: white;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease;
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-8px);
    }

    .card img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 180px;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    .card-content {
      padding: 16px;
      padding-bottom: 60px; 
    }

    .title {
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      line-height: 1.4;
      color: var(--primary-color)
    }

    .author {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--secondary-color); 
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .meta {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 12px;
      right: 12px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
      padding: 8px 16px;
      border-radius: 30px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #222;
      user-select: none;
      white-space: nowrap;
      z-index: 10; 
    }

    .meta-left {
      display: flex;
      gap: 20px;
      align-items: center;
      color: #222;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .meta-left i {
      margin-right: 6px;
      color: var(--primary-color);
      font-size: 18px; 
    }

    .btn-share {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      background-color: var(--primary-color);
      color: white;
      border: none;
      padding: 8px 16px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    
    .btn-share i {
      font-size: 18px;
      transition: 1s;
    }
    i{
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: 1s;
    }
    i:hover{
      color: #0056b3;
    }
    .btn-share:hover {
      background-color: #0056b3;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1 style="color: white;">Últimos Eventos</h1>
  <br>
  <div class="gallery">
    <div class="card">
      <img src="/images/main1.jpeg" alt="Modern Construction" />
      <div class="card-content">
        <div class="title">Consultoria Financeira Corporativa</div>
        <div class="author">Soluções estratégicas para empresas que buscam crescimento sustentável e controle total dos seus recursos.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="meta">
        <div class="meta-left">
          <div><i class="fa-solid fa-thumbs-up"></i> 185</div>
          <div><i class="fa-solid fa-eye"></i> 313</div>
        </div>
        <button class="btn-share"><i class="fa-solid fa-share"></i> Compartilhar</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <img src="/images/main2.jpeg" alt="Modern Construction" />
      <div class="card-content">
        <div class="title">Workshop: Planejamento Financeiro Pessoal</div>
        <div class="author">Evento prático para ajudar pessoas a organizarem suas finanças, reduzirem dívidas e investirem com segurança.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="meta">
        <div class="meta-left">
          <div><i class="fa-solid fa-thumbs-up"></i> 185</div>
          <div><i class="fa-solid fa-eye"></i> 313</div>
        </div>
        <button class="btn-share"><i class="fa-solid fa-share"></i> Compartilhar</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <img src="/images/main3.jpeg" alt="Modern Construction" />
      <div class="card-content">
        <div class="title">Seminário sobre Investimentos Inteligentes</div>
        <div class="author">Design elegante para eventos que ensinam a construir patrimônio com estratégias seguras e eficientes.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="meta">
        <div class="meta-left">
          <div><i class="fa-solid fa-thumbs-up"></i> 185</div>
          <div><i class="fa-solid fa-eye"></i> 313</div>
        </div>
        <button class="btn-share"><i class="fa-solid fa-share"></i> Compartilhar</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <img src="/images/main4.webp" alt="Modern Construction" />
      <div class="card-content">
        <div class="title">Programa de Mentoria para Consultores</div>
        <div class="author">Mentoria profissional para quem atua com consultoria financeira e quer elevar seus resultados.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="meta">
        <div class="meta-left">
          <div><i class="fa-solid fa-thumbs-up"></i> 185</div>
          <div><i class="fa-solid fa-eye"></i> 313</div>
        </div>
        <button class="btn-share"><i class="fa-solid fa-share"></i> Compartilhar</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <script src="/event/js/imtatic-events.js" type="text/javascript"></script>

</body>
</html>
